		<td><b>The Art Of Assembly Language</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Has anyone out there read a book called&quot;the art of assembly language&quot;, by Randall Hyde?<br />If so, would you recommend it for learning all the concepts of ASM, with the intention of taking that knowledge into 6502 programming? Just wanted to know what is the EASIEST, plain english, book to get started with programming NES games.<br />Thanks for your time and input.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


