	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd say read the nerdy nights. Then just review the instruction set entirely and anything you don't know what it does, ask. IMO, any book is a waste of 1. Money, and 2. Time, as assembly at it's core isn't difficult. It's  honestly so easy, most problems are because of overcomplication.

		

		</td>
